I.  TRAVEL DEALS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. SOUTHWEST RENEWS NATIONWIDE SALE WITH COAST-TO-COAST FARES
   FOR $178 R/T

Southwest has extended its system-wide fare sale for travel through
April 5, 2002, with cross-country fares starting at $178 round-trip
and fares within California from $78 round-trip. Purchase tickets
at least seven days before travel and by Thursday, November 1.
Other airlines have matched this sale on competing routes.

Click: http://rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.1
<A HREF="rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.1">AOL</A>

~~~~~~~~~~~~

2. VANGUARD'S SYSTEM-WIDE SAVINGS FROM $76 R/T WITH $50 COMPANION FARES



Vanguard Airlines has announced a system-wide sale with round-trip
fares starting at $76. Buy one ticket and bring a companion for $50
round-trip. Travel is available through May 16, 2002. Purchase
tickets by Wednesday, October 31. Book online and save an additional
five percent.

Click: http://rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.2
<A HREF="rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.2">AOL</A>

~~~~~~~~~~~~

3. ATA EXTENDS SALE WITH CROSS-COUNTRY FARES FROM $188 R/T

ATA has released a "fly away" sale with savings on cross-country
routes and other fares throughout its system, for travel through
February 28, 2002. Purchase tickets by Monday, October 29. Book
online and receive an additional $10 discount per round-trip
ticket. Other airlines have matched this sale on competing routes.

Click: http://rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.3
<A HREF="rd.SmarterLiving.com/da101801.3">AOL</A>

